<p class="">I understand that there is to be a debate next week. I will review the situation on Monday, but I do not want to be pressed for too many statements. I have other people to deal with, and, if I make too many statements, I reveal my mind to other people, and that makes it a little difficult.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
